metadata.name: Messhup X The Noun Square Commemorative Nouns Rose Parade Edition 1/969
metadata.description:
Today (January 2, 2023) Nouns DAO entered a float in the annual Rose Parade in Pasadena, CA. Organized by Stoopid Buddy Studios, Aubtoshi (Nouns On The Ground) and more, the event was a sensation and a memorable moment for the Nouns community! 

These stickers illustrated by Messhup depict the 3 Nouns DAO characters that adorned the float, and stickers that were printed and passed out to parade-goers. 

Mint for free as reminder of this day, on the blockchain, forever!

Watch the parade footage here on TNS YT: https://youtu.be/qvrBji5kKC4
